    </h2>
    <div class='grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2'>
      <Card class='p-6'>
        <h3 class='text-secondary mb-6 text-2xl font-bold'>Frontend</h3>
        <div class='grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3'>
